# 11. Regression Plan

Level 1

Smoke Regression

```
RESET tests
GPIO basic tests
TIMER basic tests
DMA basic tests
```

Level 2

Block Regression

```
All GPIO tests
All TIMER tests
All DMA tests
```

Level 3

SoC Regression

```
All APB tests
All AXI tests
All Interrupt tests
All Integration tests
```

---

# 12. Exit Criteria

Verification is complete when:

* All planned tests pass
* No open functional bugs
* No protocol violations
* Coverage goals achieved
* Regression passes cleanly

End of Document
